MICROCOSM TECHNO said unconsolidated sales
in December fell 47.53% to NT$34,071,000 from NT$64,934,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  12/2011          12/2010
Sales             34,071           64,934    
YOY%             -47.53%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,007,025        1,128,840   
YOY%             -10.79% 
